name: Zuckuss (V)
Lore: 'Male Gand. Practitioner of ancient religious findsman vocation. Bounty hunter and scout. Gains surprisingly accurate information through mystical visions during meditation.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Mist Hunter is maneuver +1. Your Black Sun agents at same and related sites may not have their forfeit reduced. Once per game, may deploy non-[Permanent Weapon] 4-LOM here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 3.',
